paragraphs: The best kind of vacation is when you come somewhere new and it feels like home: apartment «Artemis Apartments» is located in Kipseli. This apartment is located in walking distance from the city center. You can take a walk and explore the neighbourhood area of the apartment. Places nearby: Zakynthos Port, Port of Kyllini and Port of Argostoli.
description_struct.title: Location

paragraphs: Free Wi-Fi is available on the territory. Ask for more information when checking in. If you travel by car, you can park in a parking zone for free. You will find these entertainment amenities on the premises: a barbeque area. Swimming fans are going to enjoy a pool and an outdoor pool.
Additional services that the apartment offers to its guests: private check-in and check-out and car rental. The staff of the apartment will be happy to talk to you in English.

paragraphs: A great option for family vacation: apartment «Armonia Studios & Apartments» is located in Kipseli. This apartment is located in walking distance from the city center. You can take a walk and explore the neighbourhood area of the apartment — Zakynthos Port, Port of Kyllini and Port of Argostoli.
description_struct.title: Location

paragraphs: Spend an evening in a nice atmosphere of the bar. It’s time to have a nice meal! Stop by the restaurant. Want to be always on-line? Wi-Fi is available. If you travel by car, you can park in a parking zone.

You will find these entertainment amenities on the premises: a library, a ping-pong area and a barbeque area. Here, you can treat yourself with water procedures as there will be a pool and an outdoor pool. There are playrooms for children at the apartment. They will be having so much fun that you might have to spend the evening with adults. The tour assistance desk of the apartment will help you book an excursion.
Additional services that the apartment offers to its guests: a laundry, dry cleaning, car rental and a safe-deposit box. The staff of the apartment speaks English.
